reviewText:
I was hoping that this tape would be a compilation of actual Dan Quayle bloopers.

Instead this is a bunch of lame comedy routines poking fun of Dan Quayle.  I threw it out after one viewing.  Plus, it is only about 30 minutes long.  Avoid this like the plague.

Granted, picking on Dan Quayle's intelligence is fairly easy, but this video is hilarious.  Unless you're an extremely partisan Republican, it will deeply disturb you that this birdbrain got within a heartbeat of becoming President.  It was well worth the few dollars I spent on it.
